Package main.model

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Character
    the characters in the world the player is able to interact with
    EntityLists
    collects all entities in the game (items, objects, characters) and the player object realized as a singleton to get global access to it
    GameEntity
    Base class for all Entities in the game (items, characters and objects)
    Item
    The items contained in the world the player is allowed to take and use
    Object
    The objects contained in the world (like trees, fences, doors, houses etc.), with certain objects the user is able to interact (like open a door)
    Player
    the main character controlled by the human player
